law.text:
The Commission is not liable for the payment of interest under this subtitle:
if a proper invoice for accrued interest is not submitted within 30 days after the payment date of the amount on which the interest accrued;
for more than 1 year and 31 days after the receipt date;
on amounts representing unpaid interest; or
if the Commission determines there is a dispute regarding any material factor in the contract or purchase order.
